{
  "stem": "5388.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wasn't beating anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So those guys were pulling him, and baiting him, and he wound up with a good pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we lost our lagerfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He got pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he used to go there, and that was his day, spending looking for the girls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he used to come with-- God forbid, being alone, he use to come, and have a few men with him, and so on, to watch the cleanliness of the girls' vaginas.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That bastard.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he was gone and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Soski Agusalu.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was just a very short period of time, maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I created commotions there once.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the village of Soski Agusalu.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, we got Russian guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Russian guards, not the Estonians anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] or Estonian Russians who were ethnic Russians but were part of the free Estonia between the wars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was a translator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Suddenly, the [NON-ENGLISH] needed somebody to translate to get the farmers come with horse in places.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I go there, and I wanted to get a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the newspaper didn't come yet, so I had a Russian guard-- an Estonian Russian-- and he wanted to go dancing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said I've got to go back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The end result is I go dancing with him, and stay out till God knows what hour, was probably 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we march back-- now mind you, this is now winter, it's night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nights, you can see, you could read the paper at nighttime because it's all white nights.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we walk, we come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we come back and the Russian lieutenant, he starts [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means you bastard, you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You Jew swine, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly my lagerfuhrer calls out [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
